highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Kolkata. Jhoome Jo Pathaan is the highest at #3.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Kolkata the longest, at 68 weeks straight.
Na Ja by Pav Dharia is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kolkata, up 38 spots at #27.
Tu Mile Dil Khile by Asees Kaur and Stebin Ben is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kolkata at #11.
